/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/BLR8TiQCYAE8JJM-300x225.jpg" width="300" height="225" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://instagram.com/p/Z0RcPEvNsq/"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5875" alt="cd62ea64c6d011e2b0a322000ae9134a_7" src="http://www.wordpress-fr.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/cd62ea64c6d011e2b0a322000ae9134a_7-300x300.jpg" width="300" height="300" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://twitpic.com/ctlrly"><img class="aligncenter" alt="775318534" src="http://www.wordpress-fr.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/775318534-300x225.jpg" width="300" height="225" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://twitter.com/pippinsplugins/status/339136352190885888"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5904" alt="BLTatysCcAA7lbv" src="http://www.wordpress-fr.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/BLTatysCcAA7lbv-300x399.jpg" width="300" height="399" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://wp10.wordpress.net/2013/05/27/happy-10th-anniversary-wordpress/"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5882" alt="wpid-wp-1369667981076" src="http://www.wordpress-fr.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/wpid-wp-1369667981076-300x225.jpg" width="300" height="225" /></a></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://wp10.wordpress.net/2013/05/27/first-batch-of-drinks-for-the-paris-party/"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5909" alt="20130527-195329" src="http://www.wordpress-fr.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/20130527-195329-300x225.jpg" width="300" height="225" /></a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=C_c6dOIN_Pw:6n2c8_HQv3o:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=C_c6dOIN_Pw:6n2c8_HQv3o:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=C_c6dOIN_Pw:6n2c8_HQv3o:V_sGL